  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One killed in train collision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that a person was killed in a collision with a train last night at the Madhuranguli Sembatai section of the Puttalam-Colombo railway.",
        "According to the police, he may have collided with a passenger train coming from Colombo to Puttalam last night.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 50-year-old resident of Nikaverati Rasnayakapura area.",
        "The Madhuranguli police said that they have raised doubts as to why the deceased person had visited the Madhuranguli area and how he had collided with a train and died.",
        "The body of the victim has been kept at Puttalam Aadar Hospital for post-mortem after post-mortem."
      ],
